    "synopsis": "Across the galaxy a civil war rages, but on Terra it remains a thing of rumour and ration cuts. The Administratum adept Katanoh Tallery uncovers irregular cargo manifests above the Throneworld - ships and arms quietly siphoned to the moon of Titan under the codename Othrys - and is certain she has stumbled on a Horus-backed conspiracy at the heart of the Imperium. Hunted through the Riga Orbital Plate, she falls under the protection of Nathaniel Garro, the Knight-Errant who has been seeking the Lectitio Divinitatus saint Keeler. Together they cut through assassins and rumour to reach the truth - and find Malcador the Sigillite waiting at the top of the new fortress with answers that recast the war to come.",
